<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home/register.css">
    <script src="/js/home/register.js" defer></script>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>회원가입 하세요.</h2>
    <div class="container" id="container">
        <div class="form-container sign-up-container">
            <form action="#">
                <h1>Create Account</h1>
                <div class="social-container">
                    <a href="#" class="social"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" class="social"><i class="fab fa-google-plus-g"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" class="social"><i class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i></a>
                </div>
                <span>or use your email for registration</span>
                <input id="id" type="text" placeholder="아이디" />
                <input id="name" type="text" placeholder="닉네임" />
                <input id="psword" type="password" placeholder="비밀번호" />
                <input id="confirm-psword" type="password" placeholder="비밀번호 확인" />
                <p id="button" class="button1">Sign Up</p>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div class="overlay-container">
            <div class="overlay">
                <div class="overlay-panel overlay-left">
                    <h1>이미 아이디가 존재하나요?</h1>
                    <p>아이디가 존재하나요? 로그인 하러 가세요.</p>
                    <a href="/login"><p class="button1" id="ghost">Sign In</p></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>